      "message": "Input, and possibly output if the mask/filter impl has any special dither logic (but I can\u0027t find any evidence of such).\n\nMaybe I\u0027m overzealous with what constitutes a const paint - I\u0027m not 100% convinced the filter/mask check is needed, but it seems more conservative (and closer to what we do now) to keep it.",
